data.description: New 40-gallon water heater (2023), New waterproof scratch-resistant vinyl flooring (May 2023), New indoor/outdoor AC system (2021), Thoughtfully updated single-story gem nestled on a spacious cul-de-sac lot, just minutes away from the vibrant South Congress district, ABIA, & the bustling Downtown Austin scene. Step inside, & you'll be instantly captivated by the abundance of natural light that floods the updated interior. With vinyl plank flooring throughout, dual-pane windows, & an open floorplan, this home is designed to make daily living a breeze. The inviting entry leads you into a spacious living room, beautifully enhanced with dimmable recessed lighting, a ceiling fan, & large sliding glass doors that seamlessly connect indoor & outdoor living. Step onto the covered wood deck, where you can savor your morning coffee or host gatherings with friends, all while surrounded by the serene canopy of mature trees. The living room effortlessly flows into the eat-in kitchen, featuring elegant white shaker cabinetry & sleek stainless-steel appliances. When it's time to retreat, the primary bedroom beckons with great privacy. Two closets provide ample storage, & the private en-suite bath boasts a luxurious walk-in shower, creating a serene oasis for relaxation. The secondary bedrooms are generously sized & also feature vinyl plank flooring. They share an updated guest bath, ensuring that everyone has their own space to unwind. Outside, the possibilities are endless in the expansive yard. Whether you're looking to create your own outdoor paradise, start a garden, or simply enjoy the freedom of open space, this backyard has it all. Let's not forget the unbeatable location – with easy access to freeways, shopping, dining, & all the cultural attractions that Austin has to offer, you'll have everything you need right at your fingertips. Schedule a showing today!
